{"type":"text","value":"Jetten ","key":"AINVEefg1D"},{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","value":"et al.","key":"vau8ybO9UC"}],"key":"oCR23xGSlz"},{"type":"text","value":", 2021","key":"FbbpTUpxPl"}],"enumerator":"4","key":"H3Q5q7h3Cd"}],"key":"BgzvCoK5eD"}],"key":"wrbdfQgTlP"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":67,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Generally, Data Stewards acquire these skills through learning-on-the-job, which is facilitated by existing networks (see ","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"NJ7DNd7EZq"},{"type":"crossReference","kind":"heading","identifier":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-support","label":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-support","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Organisations that support Data Stewards","position":{"start":{"line":89,"column":1},"end":{"line":89,"column":1}},"key":"hUOM83JJYY"}],"template":"{name}","resolved":true,"html_id":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-support","key":"o8rN7lT95R"},{"type":"text","value":" below).\nThrough these networks experiences can be exchanged with peers, which is beneficial for personal and professional development.\nAn examples of these collaborative efforts is the ‘23 Things: Support for Research Data’(","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"UqlkmTRYbm"},{"type":"citeGroup","kind":"parenthetical","children":[{"type":"cite","kind":"parenthetical","label":"Jetten201923ThingsData","identifier":"jetten201923thingsdata","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Jetten ","key":"hT5Lab3ool"},{"type":"emphasis","children":[{"type":"text","value":"et al.","key":"JqcOpS97Qv"}],"key":"h78q7l7mcC"},{"type":"text","value":", 2019","key":"uOqJP70Ggi"}],"enumerator":"5","key":"NLsr7b6Pk5"}],"key":"DZKGSe789j"},{"type":"text","value":") that provides a good overview of helpful resources for Data Stewards.\nDepending on the role of the Data Steward, learning discipline specific skills may be important through contributing to specific projects or attending conferences and meetings on relevant topics.\nAs the research culture adapts to (inter)national changes, so too do the skills of the Data Steward that have to be continuously updated.","position":{"start":{"line":63,"column":1},"end":{"line":63,"column":1}},"key":"c6fTMeDzTC"}],"key":"Ps7xmXaZrJ"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1},"end":{"line":71,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Challenges for Data Stewards","position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1},"end":{"line":71,"column":1}},"key":"Cr59WuGjYf"}],"label":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-challenges","identifier":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-challenges","html_id":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-challenges","key":"E0P7ZdQyNa"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":1},"end":{"line":79,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":1},"end":{"line":72,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"As Data Steward is a relatively new profession (~2017), their job profile is not always formally defined and their career-track may be unclear.","position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":1},"end":{"line":72,"column":1}},"key":"j3xTVUiSNE"}],"key":"oVpTlfTlSO"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It is difficult to increase the awareness of the presence of the data steward and/or existing data policies, especially when resources are limited.","position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"key":"nFyFVoRPY5"}],"key":"XrnHwjfKmj"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":74,"column":1},"end":{"line":74,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It takes time to know the researchers and earn their trust, which is important to be able to adequately advise them and work together to improve data management practises.","position":{"start":{"line":74,"column":1},"end":{"line":74,"column":1}},"key":"LHEVifS2r3"}],"key":"ux8wQsiHSD"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Not everyone sees the move towards a more transparent research culture as beneficial, and you can be met with resistance from researchers that do not want to change their existing workflows.","position":{"start":{"line":75,"column":1},"end":{"line":75,"column":1}},"key":"GI58QWH98H"}],"key":"EmTGPHf3FL"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":76,"column":1},"end":{"line":77,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"There might be limited resources and time to cover all the support requests from researchers.\nOften there’s only a small central team of Data Stewards available to the entire instutite.","position":{"start":{"line":76,"column":1},"end":{"line":76,"column":1}},"key":"dqhiuxVv5B"}],"key":"owq1kJynVX"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":78,"column":1},"end":{"line":79,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It is not always clear when you’re providing high quality support and where you could improve, as there is no formal education and there is not always a strong feedback culture at your institute.","position":{"start":{"line":78,"column":1},"end":{"line":78,"column":1}},"key":"JYl9dAI0cE"}],"key":"beQxf9eIZ2"}],"key":"SKd8En4bG9"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":81,"column":1},"end":{"line":81,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Benefits of having Data Stewards","position":{"start":{"line":81,"column":1},"end":{"line":81,"column":1}},"key":"a79JmuJgjM"}],"label":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-benefits","identifier":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-benefits","html_id":"cl-infrastructure-data-stewards-benefit